name: Nole Inu
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
It is a Meme token on BSC network

What makes your project unique?
It is a meme token that will someday try to have a charity on OG of memes in Redit. And one day hoping to make a difference in crypto space

History of your project.
It is made by group of friends who have joined crypto 5 years ago. We are planning to make the name of N0LE INU trending in Crypto space. As we make a name for ourselves as well.


What’s next for your project?
We already got listed on CMC. And hopefully we will get listed in CG as well. We have done everything organically not like others who does fast track. And hopefully you will accept. And CEX listing once we grow

https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/nole-inu/

What can your token be used for?
For now it is just a meme token. But our contract is flexible that can be reduced till 0 tax which someday be used for CEX listings
